      "role": "user",
      "content": "That looks better, thanks. One last thing—since Marcus was such a strong candidate, I'm worried about him feeling like he just got lost in the shuffle of a huge pile of resumes. Could you add a final closing thought or a small concluding sentiment that makes the rejection feel a bit more 'human' and less like a robotic dismissal? Just something to soften the landing so he leaves with a good impression of our company culture.",
